{"tid":1779941,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"勇武效益越來越低，不割但應該轉 form","createTime":"2019-12-12T04:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T04:52:29.000Z","uid":38546,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"61a7a1cfbfca5c5575a90d97a2cdde35b2b56977","tid":1779941,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"和理非邊有資格割勇武。<br />\n但係依家傷嘅傷，被捕嘅被補，走佬嘅走佬。<br />\n和理非應該補位。眼見勇武效益越來越低，應該要轉 form。雖然勇武剎停咗修例，但係戰術要 be water，戰略都要 be water。勇武係手段，但係唔可以迷信勇武。將抗爭溶入生活可能係一個出路。<br />\n<br />\n1. 黃色經濟圈<br />\n2. 地區遊行 (近排少攪咗 ?)，可以攪埋地區議題，e.g. 勿摸活家禽嗰類<br />\n3. 放影會 (區議員配合 ?)<br />\n<br />\n仲有無？<br />\n一路走來都係成日諗新計新橋。但係勇武效益下降之後就頹咗？仲有無多啲和理非節目？"},{"pid":"41d26ed009f9c8a5f7b84f107c8767f501b5deb0","tid":1779941,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a551984aa933f25bb301c32063216fb30e5ee9","tid":1779941,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fdf1ed46565d43a2130f96c1ff1b317093c88a","tid":1779941,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"和你shop<br />\n就係唔夠人先要勇武<br />\n夠多人就shop得爆"},{"pid":"8fe6b03933fd92fd95c63d008923c29599175ec0","tid":1779941,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98362c121c515218da79480732ca405e14ac70b","tid":1779941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"從來個問題都係, 武裝度不足"},{"pid":"fc84fd096d5d3f42e77108366bfa5ec2234108d9","tid":1779941,"uid":38546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" 